Using this popup, you may enable or disable modification of the current
join field in UPDATE mode.

To enable modification of the join field, scroll to the desired option, 
and choose the Select menu command. 

	OPTIONS		DESCRIPTIONS
	-------		------------
	Yes		Enable modification of this field in UPDATE mode.
	No		Disable modification of this field in UPDATE mode.

The menu commands are as follows:

        MENU COMMANDS   SYNOPSIS
        -------------   --------
	Select	        Enable or disable modification of the current field
			in UPDATE mode.
			
        Cancel          Return to the JoinDef Update & Delete Rules form 
			without registering any selections.

        Help            Print this message.
